explanation.summary: Kt qu in tm  cho thy c chn on 'Block nhnh phi', nhng cc ch s khc nh nhp tim v thi gian sng QRS vn trong gii hn bnh thng.
explanation.details: Chn on 'Block nhnh phi' c ngha l tn hiu in i qua mt nhnh dn truyn c bit  tim (nhnh phi) b chm li mt cht. Theo hng dn y khoa, tnh trng ny thng lm cho sng QRS trn in tm  (phn nh hot ng in ca bung tim di) tr nn rng hn bnh thng (thng trn 0.12 giy). Tuy nhin, ch s QRS ca bn l 0.082 giy, nm trong gii hn bnh thng (<0.12 giy). Hnh nh sng in tim cho thy cc sng QRS c v hp, khng rng bt thng. Nhp tim ca bn l 73.24 nhp/pht, y l mc bnh thng.
